<div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><div class="fr-view Kanit panel-content-htmleditor"><h5>CAE-PRESS enables designers to perform a stress analysis through seamless operations of CAD and CAE.<br>Designers are only required to perform simple CAD input operations without being concerned with CAE. </h5><h5><strong>Features</strong></h5><ul><li><p><u><strong>The "StressAnalysis" command</strong></u></p></li></ul><p>Stress analyses can be performed through simple input operations.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/product/2.PRESS/02.CAE-PRESS/CAE_PRESS_01.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p> </p><ul><li><u><strong>The "StressAnalysis" command</strong></u></li></ul><p>It is possible to display and output quickly the results that have been saved after the execution of the command for stress analysis.</p><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" alt="" src="https://uelthai.co.th/uploads/product/2.PRESS/02.CAE-PRESS/CAE_PRESS_02.jpg" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p><p data-f-id="pbf" style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px; opacity: 0.65; font-family: sans-serif;">Powered by <a href="https://www.froala.com/wysiwyg-editor?pb=1" title="Froala Editor">Froala Editor</a></p></div></div>